Field	Description
Use Case ID and Name	UC-01: Start Workout



General Information




Field	Description
Description	User starts a workout session. The system generates a personalized training plan and guides the user through exercises.
Primary Actor	User
Secondary Actors	Fitness AI App (System)
Preconditions	User has access to the application; application is running; user is logged in (optional)



Main Scenario




Step	Description
1	System displays the main screen
2	User selects “Start workout”
3	System checks if personal data exists
4	System requests minimal personal data if not available
5	User enters personal data (goal, level, duration)
6	System validates entered data
7	System generates a training plan
8	System displays the training plan
9	User starts performing exercises
10	System tracks workout progress
11	User completes the workout
12	System saves results and displays summary



Alternative Scenarios




ID	Description
A1	User selects “Quick start”; system skips personal data input; system generates default training plan; system displays exercises; user starts workout



Edge Case




ID	Description
E1	System detects existing personal data and skips input steps, continuing with plan generation
E2	User starts workout without login; system allows limited functionality and generates a basic training plan
Error Scenarios




ID	Description
ER1	User enters invalid or incomplete data; system shows validation error; user corrects input; flow returns to data entry step
ER1	System fails to generate a training plan due to internal error; system shows error message and suggests retry
Postconditions




Field	Description
Postconditions	Workout session is completed; results are saved; user can view progress
Rules and Restrictions




Field	Description
Rules and Restrictions	Personal data must be valid; training plan must be generated before workout starts